To use this program you will need software able to run Python, such as IDLE.

To create the webpage follow these steps:
 - Open the file entertainment_center.py in the program IDLE.
 - Run the module via Run > Run Module (or F5)

 Running this program will generate an HTML file and automatically open it.
 The HTML file is called: fresh_tomatoes.html.

 If you want to add movies to be displayed on the website, do so in the file MovieList.py.
 Create a new Movie object for the movie you would like to add and then add it to the array - list.
